Package com.kryptonn.jba.client

Class TokenResponse

java.lang.Object
com.kryptonn.jba.client.TokenResponse
public class TokenResponse extends Object
Since:
1.0.0 TokenResponse is a class that represents the response of the OAuth authentication.

The response contains the access token, the token type and the time in seconds at which the access token will expire.

The access token is used to authenticate requests to the Battle.net API.

Version:
1.0.1
Author:
Kryptonn
